{"type":"message","id":"7156a43a","parentId":"ba87894d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T19:21:09.252Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01JCcEHCiFWPcEQh6a1RvQQN","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Docs search: session-id\r\n\r\n- [Session Management](https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session#session-management) - Session Management\r\n- [Session Tools](https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session-tool#session-tools) - Session Tools\r\n- [Session ids \\(sessionId\\)](https://docs.openclaw.ai/reference/session-management-compaction#session-ids-sessionid) - Session ids \\(sessionId\\)\r\n- [Sessions](https://docs.openclaw.ai/gateway/cli-backends#sessions) - sessions, set sessionArg \\(e.g. --<mark><b>session-id</b></mark> \\) or\r\n- [Session Pruning](https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session-pruning#session-pruning) - Session Pruning\r\n- [Session mapping](https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/acp#session-mapping) - Session mapping\r\n- [tools.sessions](https://docs.openclaw.ai/gateway/configuration-reference#tools-sessions) - tools.sessions\r\n- [Sessions](https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/agent#sessions) - Sessions\r\n- [Session Files](https://docs.openclaw.ai/pi#session-files) - Session Files\r\n- [Routing & Sessions](https://docs.openclaw.ai/channels/msteams#routing-&-sessions) - Routing &amp; Sessions"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5130,"aggregated":"# Docs search: session-id\r\n\r\n- [Session Management](https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session#session-management) - Session Management\r\n- [Session Tools](https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session-tool#session-tools) - Session Tools\r\n- [Session ids \\(sessionId\\)](https://docs.openclaw.ai/reference/session-management-compaction#session-ids-sessionid) - Session ids \\(sessionId\\)\r\n- [Sessions](https://docs.openclaw.ai/gateway/cli-backends#sessions) - sessions, set sessionArg \\(e.g. --<mark><b>session-id</b></mark> \\) or\r\n- [Session Pruning](https://docs.ope