{"type":"message","id":"5541ec4d","parentId":"187a20ad","timestamp":"2026-04-03T19:21:19.479Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01NSjaKcT5Ch7vu3zu9Xqxhg","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.1 (da64a97) — Like having a senior engineer on call, except I don't bill hourly or sigh audibly.\r\n\r\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\r\n\r\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\r\n\r\nOptions:\r\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\r\n\r\nCommands:\r\n  add         Add a cron job\r\n  disable     Disable a cron job\r\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\r\n  enable      Enable a cron job\r\n  help        Display help for command\r\n  list        List cron jobs\r\n  rm          Remove a cron job\r\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\r\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\r\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\r\n\r\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\r\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1954,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.1 (da64a97) — Like having a senior engineer on call, except I don't bill hourly or sigh audibly.\r\n\r\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\r\n\r\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\r\n\r\nOptions:\r\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\r\n\r\nCommands:\r\n  add         Add a cron job\r\n  disable     Disable a cron job\r\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\r\n  enable      Enable a cron job\r\n  help        Display help for command\r\n  list        List cron jobs\r\n  rm          Remove a cron job\r\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\r\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\r\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\r\n\r\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\r\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.","cwd":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":17